

 SUSPECT - PARTY ZONE III
 ------------------------

 We have pleasure in informing you that, for the third consecutive year,
 the SUSPECT group will organize in Brest a meeting wholly dedicated to
 Amiga and its environment .


 GENERAL INFORMATIONS
 --------------------


 DATE :

 From the 26th to the 27th of august 1995 . 
 The meeting will start about 10 AM on saturday morning till sunday 
 evening .


 PLACE :

 ECOLE SAINTE-ANNE / 20 RUE DE LA MOTTE-PICQUET / 29200 BREST / FRANCE
 
 A main room, with all necessary conveniences (wc, cloackrooms, video,
 distributors), will be at the members disposal as well as other
 several rooms for the rest of everyone .

 From the station or from the Place de la liberte (main place of the
 city), the bus service *5 will allow you to reach the school without
 any difficulty . You will have to get down at the bus stop called
 Place Albert 1er - Fac de medecine then you walked down to the
 crossroads and the school is just further on the left .
 The journey from the station to the school by bus will only take
 about ten minutes .
 For the walk's fanatics, take the Clemenceau Avenue until the Place
 de la liberte, then take the Foch Avenue which will directly lead
 you to the Place Albert 1er not far from the school .


 PRICES :

 60 FF (Amiga,monitor and cables) / On the spot : 70 FF (Amiga ...)
 80 FF (in the opposite case)                     90 FF


 COMPOS :

 ACCORDING TO THE MEMBER'S PREFERENCE

 An entire liberty will be let to each group as for the choice of
 the production to present (Demo, Intro ...), the aim is above all
 to take part in . Of course, the winnings will be here to reward
 the novelty (and not the prestige) of each one . Note that this
 year a special prize will be attributed to the most pleasant group
 of the meeting .

 Each production will have to work on a standard configuration
 (A1200 2 Mb Chip / 0 Mb Fast . The size of the exe.file is not
 stated (avoid the intros 40 Kb) .
 The more members we have, the more domains we cover and of course
 the more important the rewards will be ...

    
 SPONSORS :

 The sponsors will be numerous this year (Mac Donald of Coat ar
 Gueven,Phill Pizz?, La Cave du Chateau, Shopi ...) . We are also
 going to get in touch with our faithful retailers (Materiels,
 Peripheriques, and DP ...) and the fanatics' journals .


 ADD :

 INVITATIONS AND INFORMATIONS

 We realized with the experience, that the invitations for the
 meeting should be paid up before the working-out of this one
 in order, on one hand, to know how many people will participate
 (this precaution allow to avoid the withdrawals of last moment)
 and, on the other hand, to allow us to set rapidly the awarding .

 Please send your correct details (with the assumed name of your
 group) as well as you will to participate to one or several
 competitives of the SUSPECT meeting to the following address * :

 Mr Yann HUGUEN
