 GENERAL CONDITIONS
 ------------------

 The spirit which made the sucess of the meeting will be retained . We can't
 and we don't want to pretend to a party as somptuous as the Saturne Party
 III . In a way , we complement this kind of event in a different style, in
 a convivial atmosphere and in a more qualified spirit of competition .
 In this respect, we would like to thank Tobias Richter, Doh, What has been
 DARK DEMON, OPUS MAG, all the team of the NGC group, the DEMONIAC group,
 the RAC members and number of persons because they had appreciated the
 organisation of the SUSPECT meeting which is a 'family ' organisation which
 owe a lot to its members and to the devotion of its circle .

 At last, the SUSPECT group releases itself from all responsability
 concerning thefts and others offences (illicit copies for instance) which
 may happen during the meeting but informs the members that all offence will
 be punished by the immediate exclusion of this one .


 NOTE : Alow some change and adaptators .


